TORAY PLANS $ 150 MLN CZECH DYE PLANT - CTK . Japan - based Toray Industries Inc . , has agreed to build a new textile dye plant in the Czech Republic city of Prostejov , with planned greenfield investment estimated at $ 150 million , the Czech news agency CTK said on Thursday . It quoted the head of the Czech state - funded investment support agency Czechinvest , Jan Havelka , as saying that the new plant would consist of a fully - automated textile dye and weaving operation in the eastern Czech city , which is the country ' s main centre of textile production . Further details were not yet available . - - Prague Newsroom , 42 - 2 - 2423 - 0003 
